&lt;h2 id="get-meeting-attendance-report-through-graph-powershell">Get Meeting Attendance Report Through Graph PowerShell
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>Since we&amp;rsquo;re accessing data without a signed in user, we need an Entra ID application with appropriate application permissions.&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="create-a-new-entra-id-app-registration">Create a new Entra ID App Registration.
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>Note: You&amp;rsquo;ll need Global Admin access to grant the consent for your organization.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Go to the &lt;a class="link" href="https://entra.microsoft.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Entra ID Portal&lt;/a> and click on &lt;strong>App registrations&lt;/strong> under &lt;strong>Applications&lt;/strong> in the left navigation menu.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://heusser.pro/p/get-microsoft-teams-meeting-attendance-report-through-graph-api-lhpctbnzht7z/image-4.png"
