loading="lazy"
decoding="async"
alt="App registrations"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="46"
data-flex-basis="111px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Then click &lt;strong>+ New registration&lt;/strong>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://heusser.pro/p/get-microsoft-teams-meeting-attendance-report-through-graph-api-lhpctbnzht7z/image-5.png"
width="1224"
height="190"
