>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Give your app registration a name and keep &lt;strong>Accounts in this organizational directory only (&amp;ldquo;Org Name&amp;rdquo; only - Single tenant)&lt;/strong>. Under &lt;strong>Redirect URI (optional)&lt;/strong> select &lt;strong>Public client/native (mobile &amp;amp; desktop)&lt;/strong> and enter &lt;code>http://localhost&lt;/code> as redirect URI.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://heusser.pro/p/get-microsoft-teams-meeting-attendance-report-through-graph-api-lhpctbnzht7z/image-6.png"
