>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Click &lt;strong>Register&lt;/strong> to create the app registration.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Copy the &lt;strong>Application (client) ID&lt;/strong> and the &lt;strong>Directory (tenant ID)&lt;/strong>. You&amp;rsquo;ll need this later.&lt;/p>
