&lt;h4 id="results">Results
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>Once the Application Access Policy already exists and was already granted to the organizer, the console output looks much less cluttered. The report will be saved to the current directory and it&amp;rsquo;s filename will include the subject of the meeting.&lt;/p>
