>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>If there are multiple attendance reports for a meeting, like when a meeting already ended and someone joined again after that or when it&amp;rsquo;s a recurring meeting, all reports will be combined into a single CSV. The CSV does include the report id in the last column.&lt;/p>
